'''Benjamin Tahirović''' ({{IPA|bs|běɲamin tâːxiroʋitɕ|pron}}; born 3 March 2003) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Midfielder#Defensive midfielder|defensive midfielder]] for [[Danish Superliga]] club [[Brøndby IF|Brøndby]]. Born in Sweden, he plays for the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina national team]].

Tahirović started his professional career at [[Vasalunds IF]], before joining [[AS Roma|Roma]] in 2021. Two years later, he moved to [[AFC Ajax|Ajax]]. In 2025, he was transferred to Brøndby.

Tahirović made his senior international debut for Bosnia and Herzegovina in 2023, earning over 20 [[Cap (sport)|caps]] since.

==Club career==

===Early career===
Tahirović started playing football at his hometown club [[AIK Fotboll|AIK]], before joining the youth setup of FC Djursholm in 2017. In 2020, he switched to [[Vasalunds IF]]. He made his professional debut against [[IFK Berga]] on 14 June 2020 at the age of 17.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://reprezentacija.ba/379580-mourinhov-biser-s-bosanskom-dusom-brat-mu-je-prije-tri-godine-igrao-u-bih|title=Mourinhov biser s bosanskom dušom: Brat mu je prije tri godine igrao u BiH|website=reprezentacija.ba|date=16 January 2023|access-date=16 January 2023|language=bs}}</ref>

===Roma===
In February 2021, Tahirović was transferred to Italian side [[AS Roma|Roma]] for an undisclosed fee.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://fokus.ba/sport/fudbal/benjamin-tahirovic-potpisao-za-romu-u-prostorijama-kluba-ga-docekao-dzeko/1985532|title=Benjamin Tahirović potpisao za Romu, u prostorijama kluba ga dočekao Džeko|website=fokus.ba|date=1 February 2021|access-date=1 February 2021|language=bs}}</ref> He made his official debut for the team against [[Torino FC|Torino]] on 13 November 2022.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://avaz.ba/sport/nogomet/786306/benjamin-tahirovic-debitovao-za-prvi-tim-rome|title=Benjamin Tahirović debitovao za prvi tim Rome|website=avaz.ba|date=13 November 2022|access-date=16 November 2022|language=bs}}</ref>

===Ajax===
[[File:Benjamin Tahirović - GAE - Ajax (53465349575).jpg|thumb|upright|Tahirović with [[AFC Ajax|Ajax]] in 2024]]

In June 2023, Tahirović signed a five-year deal with Dutch outfit [[AFC Ajax|Ajax]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://raport.ba/benjamin-tahirovic-novi-igrac-ajaxa-potpisao-ugovor-do-2028-godine|title=Benjamin Tahirović novi igrač Ajaxa, potpisao ugovor do 2028. godine|website=raport.ba|date=21 June 2023|access-date=24 June 2023|language=bs}}</ref> He made his competitive debut for the squad on 12 August against [[Heracles Almelo|Heracles]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://reprezentacija.ba/397884-benjamin-tahirovic-igrao-od-prve-minute-i-majstorski-asistirao-u-zvanicnom-debiju-za-ajax|title=Tahirović igrao od prve minute i majstorski asistirao u zvaničnom debiju za Ajax|website=reprezentacija.ba|date=12 August 2023|access-date=12 August 2023|language=bs}}</ref> On 12 November, he scored his first professional goal against [[Almere City FC|Almere City]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://klix.ba/sport/nogomet/tahirovic-od-junaka-do-tragicara-postigao-prvijenac-za-ajax-pa-u-94-minuti-kostao-svoj-tim-pobjede/231112068|title=Tahirović od junaka do tragičara: Postigao prvijenac za Ajax pa u 94. minuti koštao svoj tim pobjede|website=klix.ba|date=12 November 2023|access-date=12 November 2023|language=bs}}</ref>

===Brøndby===
In February 2025, Tahirović moved to Danish team [[Brøndby IF|Brøndby]] on a contract until June 2028.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://faktor.ba/sport/fudbal/tahirovic-u-brondbyju-do-ljeta-2028-mlad-je-ima-nevjerovatnu-tehniku-i-priliku-za-daljnji-razvoj/210206|title=Tahirović u Brøndbyju do ljeta 2028.: Mlad je, ima nevjerovatnu tehniku i priliku za daljnji razvoj|website=faktor.ba|date=4 February 2025|access-date=4 February 2025|language=bs}}</ref> He debuted officially for the side against [[Viborg FF]] on 14 February.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://n1info.ba/sport/nogomet/tahirovic-upisao-zvanicni-debi-za-brondby|title=Tahirović upisao zvanični debi za Brøndby|website=n1info.ba|date=14 February 2025|access-date=16 February 2025|language=bs}}</ref> On 27 October, he scored his first goal for Brøndby in a triumph over [[Odense Boldklub|Odense]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportske.ba/clanak/majstorija-benjamina-tahirovic-za-prvi-gol-u-dresu-brondbya|title=Majstorija Benjamina Tahirović za prvi gol u dresu Brøndbya|website=sportske.ba|date=27 October 2025|access-date=27 October 2025|language=bs}}</ref>

==International career==
In March 2023, Tahirović received his first senior call up to [[Bosnia and Herzegovina national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina]], for [[UEFA Euro 2024 qualifying Group J|UEFA Euro 2024 qualifiers]] against [[Iceland national football team|Iceland]] and [[Slovakia national football team|Slovakia]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://fokus.ba/sport/fudbal/hadzibegic-pozvao-25-igraca-na-spisku-tahirovic-i-jedno-veliko-iznenadjenje/2514137|title=Hadžibegić pozvao 25 igrača: Na spisku Tahirović i jedno veliko iznenađenje|website=fokus.ba|date=8 March 2023|access-date=8 March 2023|language=bs}}</ref> He debuted against the former on 23 March.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://scsport.ba/savrsen-start-kvalifikacija-za-ep-zmajevi-razbili-island-prvijenac-fenomenalnog-dedica|title=Savršen start kvalifikacija za EP: Zmajevi razbili Island, prvijenac fenomenalnog Dedića|website=scsport.ba|date=23 March 2023|access-date=24 March 2023|language=bs}}</ref>

On 6 September 2025, in a [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – UEFA Group H|2026 FIFA World Cup qualifier]] against [[San Marino national football team|San Marino]], he scored his first senior international goal.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://reprezentacija.ba/481613-zmajevi-razbili-san-marino-u-gostima|title=Zmajevi razbili San Marino u gostima|website=reprezentacija.ba|date=6 September 2025|access-date=9 September 2025|language=bs}}</ref>

In June 2026, Tahirović was named in Bosnia and Herzegovina's squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportske.ba/clanak/barbarez-poslao-konacan-spisak-fifa-i-jedno-ime-otputovalo-u-ameriku-ali-nije-na-listi|title=Barbarez poslao konačan spisak FIFA-i: Jedno ime otputovalo u Ameriku, ali nije na listi|website=sportske.ba|date=3 June 2026|access-date=3 June 2026|language=bs}}</ref>

==Personal life==
Tahirović is a practising [[Islam|Muslim]]; together with international teammates [[Ermedin Demirović]], [[Jusuf Gazibegović]], [[Haris Tabaković]], [[Nihad Mujakić]], [[Haris Hajradinović]], [[Dženis Burnić]], [[Sead Kolašinac]], [[Enver Kulašin]], [[Nail Omerović]], [[Osman Hadžikić]] and [[Ermin Bičakčić]] he visited a [[mosque]] in [[Ilidža]] during the national team's concentration.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sportsport.ba/fudbal/prvo-dzuma-a-onda-put-za-zenicu-bh-reprezentativci-iznenadili-prisutne-u-dzamiji-na-ilidzi/483813|title=Prvo džuma, a onda put za Zenicu: Bh. reprezentativci iznenadili prisutne u džamiji na Ilidži|website=sportsport.ba|date=11 October 2024|access-date=12 October 2024|language=bs}}</ref>

